<div class="paragraph">
<p>Alternatively, go to <strong>plentymarkets Logo (Start) » My account</strong> and click on <span class="icon darkGrey"><i class="fa fa-life-ring  "></i></span> <strong>Support-Hotline</strong>.
Information about the support hotline is displayed in a pop-up window.</p>
</div>
