</div><h1 id="60" class="sect0">Service (partially chargeable; all editions)</h1><div class="paragraph">
<p>You didn’t find the right contact option yet and don’t really know who can assist you with your problem or your question? This is where our service team comes into play, which coordinates all kinds of requests and makes sure that you’re directed to the right place. Even smaller technical issues will be solved quickly and free of charge. In this case, get in touch via <a href="mailto:service@plentymarkets.com">service@plentymarkets.com</a> or directly contact us by phone.</p>
</div><div class="paragraph">
<p>We’re available for you:<br>
Mon – Fri from 8 am – 6 pm (UTC + 2)<br>
Telephone: +49 561 98 681 100</p>
